{
  "stem": "16790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was rather interesting because there was so much food aboard the ship that it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, first class food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I couldn't cut my own meat because, you know, I was a little boy, and so the waiter-- and they were very, very nice people-- the waiter cut my food for me and I could eat it then.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my mother could not-- never leave the stateroom because of sickness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she-- she warned me, don't you go down-- in your wanderings around the ship, don't you go down to the engine room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, naturally the first place I headed was the engine room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was intrigued by the machinery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The engine room was where all of the die-hard Nazis were working.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And she didn't-- she-- I guess she must have known that because-- but they were-- they didn't bother me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, I remember walking around and looking down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had like a little catwalk where you could stand and look down on-- on all the moving parts.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The pistons and the piston rods were moving and I was just intrigued by this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I went all over the ship all by myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was fascinating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then once we put to sea, it was even more interesting because I had-- I had so much freedom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had never tasted freedom like that before in my whole life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Yes, they sang songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess-- I never saw this, but I guess in certain cases, they made life a little bit rough on some of the people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They, you know, they'd give this heil Hitler salute and, you know, just to bring back memories to-- to these Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were 937 Jews aboard the ship.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
